snippet.title: The Garden Path - release window trailer
snippet.description:
The Garden Path is a slice-of-life sim about the joy of gardening, and the small pleasures that follow. Coming to PC, Linux and Nintendo Switch in late Spring 2024.

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1638500/The_Garden_Path/
